          <h2>Physical Characteristics</h2>
          <p>Uranus is the third-largest planet by diameter and fourth-largest by mass. Its physical properties reflect its status as an ice giant with a fundamentally different internal structure than the gas giants.</p>

          <div class="info-box glass">
            <h3>Uranus Quick Facts</h3>
            <ul>
