          <h2>Interesting Facts About Uranus</h2>
          <p>Uranus's unique characteristics make it one of the most peculiar planets in our solar system.</p>

          <ul class="facts-list">
            <li><strong>First Planet Discovered with a Telescope:</strong> Uranus was the first planet discovered in modern times, expanding the known solar system beyond the five planets visible to the naked eye. Its discovery by William Herschel in 1781 demonstrated that systematic observation could reveal previously unknown worlds.</li>

